[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 2.0"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 2.0 are now fixed in Tails 2.0.1.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to Tails 2.0.1|news/version_2.0.1]] as soon as possible.

Details
=======

* Tor Browser: [[!mfsa 2016-13]], [[!mfsa 2016-14]]
* virtualbox: [[!debsa2016 3454]]
* curl: [[!debsa2016 3455]]
* openjdk-7: [[!debsa2016 3458]]
* krb5: [[!debsa2016 3466]]
* tiff: [[!debsa2016 3467]]
